WEBVTT

00:11.750 --> 00:13.041
I'm Anderson Cooper.

00:13.125 --> 00:16.583
I'm rich, I'm hot,
I don't need this.

00:16.667 --> 00:18.166
Earlier tonight, President Trump

00:18.250 --> 00:19.166
released his
March Madness bracket.

00:19.250 --> 00:22.375
- Take a look.
- Big fan of March Madness.

00:22.458 --> 00:25.667
It will distract Americans
while I pay off Stormy Daniels

00:25.750 --> 00:28.625
by making her
my top economic adviser.

00:28.709 --> 00:29.667
She's got big shoes to fill.

00:29.750 --> 00:32.875
No one put out for billionaires
like Gary Cohn.

00:32.959 --> 00:36.583
Anyways, my March Madness
prediction... Bulls in seven.

00:36.667 --> 00:38.166
Wow. I'm being told

00:38.250 --> 00:40.375
the leader of the free world
is on the line?

00:40.458 --> 00:42.166
Hey, Anderson,
this trade war's gonna be fun!

00:42.250 --> 00:45.166
You ready to pay 50 bucks
for a stapler?

00:45.250 --> 00:47.458
What's going on with
your steel tariffs?

00:47.542 --> 00:48.709
Get ready!

00:48.792 --> 00:51.625
Buildings swaying in the breeze
like fields of wheat.

00:51.709 --> 00:54.500
How do you respond to reports
of chaos in the White House?

00:54.583 --> 00:58.000
Don't for a second believe that
this White House is in chaos.

00:58.083 --> 01:00.291
We're like
a well-oiled tornado.

01:00.375 --> 01:02.792
Any thoughts on Ted Cruz
winning his primary?

01:02.875 --> 01:05.333
Before this decade is out,
we will make Ted Cruz

01:05.417 --> 01:08.750
the first man to involuntarily
walk on the Moon!

01:08.834 --> 01:11.750
Jesus.
When we come back,

01:11.834 --> 01:13.834
who will be the next sycophant
to blow this wide open?

01:13.917 --> 01:18.875
Hey! Anderson!
Am I gonna be on the show?!

01:18.959 --> 01:21.625
Ted Cruz has won his
primary and stands ready

01:21.709 --> 01:24.750
to earn your vote to return
to the United States Senate.

01:24.834 --> 01:27.542
He supports a flat tax of 0.0%

01:27.625 --> 01:30.417
and believes the only way
to stop a bad guy with a gun

01:30.500 --> 01:32.000
is 20 good teachers
shooting guns

01:32.083 --> 01:33.000
like out-of-control fire hoses.

01:33.083 --> 01:35.041
And to America's
next generation,

01:35.125 --> 01:37.166
Ted Cruz won't just
pay you lip service.

01:37.250 --> 01:40.500
He'll be your personal
"A Wrinkle in Time" god

01:40.583 --> 01:43.834
ready to fold time and space
to find your dad.

01:43.917 --> 01:46.417
The freedom of
a golden chalice of horse,

01:46.500 --> 01:47.291
horse liberty, and freedom

01:47.375 --> 01:49.834
riding along
according to the Bible

01:49.917 --> 01:50.834
and the Lord and the values.

01:50.917 --> 01:53.041
And so forth.

01:53.125 --> 01:54.709
This message has been paid for
and approved by...

01:54.792 --> 01:56.250
a-Ted Cruz!

01:56.333 --> 01:58.500
Ted Cruz! Ted Cruz! Ted Cruz!
Ted Cruz! Ta-doo da-doh!

02:01.750 --> 02:03.750
Unh! Oof!

02:11.291 --> 02:15.083
President Trump
is in North Dakota

02:15.166 --> 02:17.709
for a cam... paign-style rally,

02:17.792 --> 02:19.583
cele... brating the completion

02:19.667 --> 02:22.375
of a colossal frito pie
in his likeness.

02:22.458 --> 02:24.208
The media has been
cordoned into a pen

02:24.291 --> 02:28.208
usually reserved
for pig insemination.

02:28.291 --> 02:29.208
And reporters
have already been menaced

02:29.291 --> 02:33.041
and, in one unfortunate case,
inseminated.

02:33.125 --> 02:37.000
Fox News' Ed Henry is expecting.

02:37.083 --> 02:40.166
Mazel tov on your
gestating man-beast.

02:40.250 --> 02:41.500
Let's go there live.

02:41.583 --> 02:43.250
Wow.

02:43.333 --> 02:44.625
We're having a great time,
right, folks?

02:44.709 --> 02:48.458
Look at all those people in the
back hiding behind the cameras,

02:48.542 --> 02:51.083
broadcasting real things
I say and do.

02:51.166 --> 02:52.333
What do we call them?

02:52.417 --> 02:54.458
Fake news!

02:54.542 --> 02:55.750
That's right!

02:55.834 --> 02:56.417
And they won't tell you this,

02:56.500 --> 02:57.500
but I was born and raised

02:57.583 --> 03:01.333
right here in North Dakota
under these bleachers!

03:01.417 --> 03:05.583
The land beneath your feet
was my playground.

03:05.667 --> 03:08.041
And what the hell?
I'm 90% Sioux Indian!

03:08.125 --> 03:10.250
- Yeah!
- Make America great again!

03:10.333 --> 03:13.458
And you know what?
The lying media also

03:13.542 --> 03:16.834
won't admit that my poll numbers
are through the frickin' roof!

03:16.917 --> 03:18.917
We're talking
Gaddafi in his prime!

03:19.000 --> 03:20.917
Look, I don't even have a TV.

03:21.000 --> 03:22.709
I mean, I'm more of a book guy.

03:22.792 --> 03:23.625
I breast-fed my boys.

03:23.709 --> 03:26.291
I started the whole
undershirt trend.

03:26.375 --> 03:29.667
I was conceived when
the first atomic bomb dropped

03:29.750 --> 03:32.333
and born when
the second one dropped!

03:32.417 --> 03:33.959
- Whoo!
- Yeah!

03:34.041 --> 03:36.250
All you crowbar owners,

03:36.333 --> 03:39.333
I'm not calling for violence
against the media,

03:39.417 --> 03:43.792
but let me just say that
their skulls are full of candy!

03:46.542 --> 03:48.458
Setting aside that
the President said

03:48.542 --> 03:51.250
members of the press
"make good ingredients,"

03:51.333 --> 03:53.792
does he stand behind
his repeated lies?

03:53.875 --> 03:55.458
It's the position
of this administration

03:55.542 --> 03:57.250
that everything
the President says is true

03:57.333 --> 03:59.083
or becomes true
the moment he says it.

03:59.166 --> 04:02.125
So you won't admit that the
President misspoke when he said

04:02.208 --> 04:04.375
there's never been
a movie about lawyers?

04:04.458 --> 04:06.083
The President
will not be hamstrung

04:06.166 --> 04:08.583
by the arbitrary,
half-baked concept of logic.

04:08.667 --> 04:09.750
Oh,
you got to be kidding.

04:09.834 --> 04:11.125
- Come on!
- Jesus Christ.

04:11.208 --> 04:13.000
And up next on
the "The Ridiculist,"

04:13.083 --> 04:15.583
is Trump's presidency
rolling away from him?

04:15.667 --> 04:18.333
According to Melania's eyes,
it is.

04:18.416 --> 04:20.875
Take a look at this eye-roll
during the President's speech.

04:20.959 --> 04:23.542
Ugh. Here's what our CNN
eye-language expert had to say.

04:23.625 --> 04:26.166
Well, the First Lady's eye-roll
tells me that she thinks

04:26.250 --> 04:28.834
her husband is in over his head.

04:28.917 --> 04:30.333
Also, she's unhappy

04:30.417 --> 04:33.166
because he calls the ice-cream
freezer his real wife.

04:33.250 --> 04:34.834
Wow.
He's perceptive.

04:34.917 --> 04:37.750
Melania, I want you
to answer me honestly.

04:37.834 --> 04:39.000
Were those your eyes?

04:39.083 --> 04:42.959
Yes, but cut me some slack.
I-I just did it once.

04:43.041 --> 04:45.000
That's just the start.
Take a look.

04:45.083 --> 04:46.792
Name one Italian person

04:46.875 --> 04:49.208
who doesn't like meatballs.

04:49.291 --> 04:52.208
I used to be the
face of Neutrogena.

04:52.291 --> 04:54.375
I made Oprah wear
all that weird shit

04:54.458 --> 04:56.875
for that
"A Wrinkle in Time" movie.

04:56.959 --> 05:00.667
All right, I did it a lot,
but I can't control it.

05:00.750 --> 05:03.625
It's like how you can't talk
to someone in leg braces

05:03.709 --> 05:04.542
without commenting
on them.

05:04.625 --> 05:07.625
Honey, whenever your face
undermines me,

05:07.709 --> 05:10.375
it makes my job even harder
than it already is.

05:10.458 --> 05:12.917
Now let's watch another
seven hours of TV.

05:13.000 --> 05:15.041
All I ever
hear around here is no.

05:15.125 --> 05:17.291
Look, nuking the ocean

05:17.375 --> 05:18.291
is the only way we're
gonna get rid of the sharks.

05:18.375 --> 05:20.709
Sir, I wouldn't
bring this up

05:20.792 --> 05:22.709
if not for the graveness
of the situation,

05:22.792 --> 05:24.250
but I believe we may
have a media problem.

05:24.333 --> 05:25.375
- Who cares?
- What is the matter?

05:25.458 --> 05:28.667
I think the paperboy
is in love with my wife.

05:28.750 --> 05:31.208
But you've been saying my press
is great ever since I fired

05:31.291 --> 05:33.875
your predecessor for
saying I had bad press.

05:34.000 --> 05:36.000
I've been operating
under the assumption

05:36.083 --> 05:37.291
that "great" means
"a dizzying amount."

05:37.375 --> 05:40.041
The major networks
are simulcasting

05:40.125 --> 05:41.500
a star-studded benefit
to bribe you to quit,

05:41.583 --> 05:44.166
and The Washington Post
changed their slogan

05:44.250 --> 05:46.083
from "Democracy
dies in darkness"

05:46.166 --> 05:47.417
to "Democracy died,

05:47.500 --> 05:50.125
and the President is
balls-deep in the corpse."

05:51.333 --> 05:54.583
Donald, did you know
Jackie O

05:54.667 --> 05:58.333
never rolled her eyes once
during JFK's speeches?

05:58.417 --> 06:00.417
I want to be like that,

06:00.500 --> 06:03.583
the Washington woman with a face
like a haunted mansion,

06:03.667 --> 06:09.083
a beautiful exterior concealing
screaming ghouls inside.

06:09.166 --> 06:10.250
That's great, Melania.

06:10.333 --> 06:11.917
I don't need to know
what's inside you

06:12.000 --> 06:13.083
any more than I need to know
what's inside my book.

06:13.166 --> 06:15.667
Can you find someone
to teach me?

06:15.750 --> 06:20.458
Of course. And the effort will
be so worth it, believe me.

06:20.542 --> 06:21.667
You know,
I've come this far

06:21.750 --> 06:24.000
only because
I don't show my emotions.

06:24.083 --> 06:26.959
What the fuck? Who the hell
moved my goddamn Ring Pop?!

06:27.041 --> 06:28.500
I'm gonna kill somebody!

06:28.583 --> 06:31.125
All right, people.

06:31.208 --> 06:33.625
I need an update
on the signature legislation

06:33.709 --> 06:35.625
that will define my legacy...

06:35.709 --> 06:39.959
The bill that finally reduces
the air in potato-chip bags.

06:40.041 --> 06:42.125
Last week, I lobbied
Congressional leaders,

06:42.208 --> 06:45.667
and they all said, "If baby
wants his bottle, then fine."

06:45.750 --> 06:48.291
I believe they were
complimenting your
youthful skin.

06:48.375 --> 06:50.458
That was last week,
before the media

06:50.542 --> 06:52.166
completely turned on you
and pilloried the bill.

06:52.250 --> 06:54.625
What?
Are you kidding me?

06:54.709 --> 06:57.125
That legislation was the only
hill I was willing to die on.

06:57.208 --> 06:58.750
Well, you should've
thought of that

06:58.834 --> 07:00.333
before you
called on supporters

07:00.417 --> 07:02.166
to make furniture out of
the media's bones.

07:02.250 --> 07:03.500
If I let them derail
my potato-chip agenda,

07:03.583 --> 07:05.625
I won't be able
to look at the man I see

07:05.709 --> 07:09.709
in the two gigantic mirrors
placed side by side!

07:09.792 --> 07:11.417
Melania,
you asked for someone

07:11.500 --> 07:14.542
who could teach you
to hide your emotions,

07:14.625 --> 07:16.417
so I searched the world,
and lo and behold,

07:16.500 --> 07:19.792
the perfect person
was down the hall

07:19.875 --> 07:23.208
and fit perfectly
under our bed sheet.

07:23.291 --> 07:26.667
Press secretary
Sarah Huckabee Sanders!

07:26.750 --> 07:29.333
Look at that blank face.
She's not even mad

07:29.417 --> 07:31.291
that I had her stand
under that sheet all night.

07:31.375 --> 07:33.250
When I'm done with you,
your face will not show

07:33.333 --> 07:35.583
guilt, shame,
joy, or fury.

07:35.667 --> 07:38.000
Instead, it will be an
unconquerable fortress

07:38.083 --> 07:38.917
covered in rocks
and spikes.

07:39.041 --> 07:41.542
It's beautiful.

07:41.625 --> 07:43.542
Dad, you got to put the media
in their place,

07:43.625 --> 07:46.291
or they'll just, like,
bark and shit

07:46.375 --> 07:48.625
all over the house
like Eric.
Yeah!

07:48.709 --> 07:51.875
I can't manipulate the
entire media. It's huge.

07:51.959 --> 07:53.750
There's like four news channels,
three newspapers,

07:53.834 --> 07:57.875
plus Lonnie and the whole
104.5 morning zoo crew.

07:57.959 --> 08:00.583
The media may be huge,
but you're hugerer.

08:00.667 --> 08:01.792
You need to bribe them,
manipulate them,

08:01.875 --> 08:05.000
be the guy who extorted
a New York Post reporter

08:05.083 --> 08:06.792
so they'd say you're
good at tennis.

08:06.875 --> 08:08.458
Yeah! The guy who convinced
The Village Voice

08:08.542 --> 08:13.083
to declare you the
Downtown Club Queen of 1986!

08:13.166 --> 08:14.709
The guy who called
The Wall Street Journal

08:14.792 --> 08:17.917
posing as a talking money clip
upset about how hard it was

08:18.000 --> 08:19.250
to hold all your cash.

08:19.333 --> 08:22.250
Ah, good old Clippo.
You're right, Don.

08:22.333 --> 08:24.583
The press shouldn't be allowed
to say whatever it wants

08:24.667 --> 08:25.750
as much as I'm not allowed
to say whatever I want.

08:25.834 --> 08:28.583
I'm only allowed to say
what my brain tells my mouth,

08:28.667 --> 08:31.333
and the media
should be no different.

08:31.417 --> 08:32.917
Fuck yeah!
All of that!

