contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

08:42.708 --> 08:46.792
President Trump has summoned
prominent media figures

08:46.875 --> 08:49.500
to the White House to rebuild
the damaged relation... ship.

08:49.583 --> 08:52.709
I was told to stay home,
but that's okay,

08:52.792 --> 08:54.750
because my wife
is my best friend,

08:54.834 --> 08:56.583
and we have great conversations.

08:56.667 --> 08:58.375
Wow. Look at this.
Isn't this tremendous?

08:58.458 --> 09:00.417
Isn't it cozy?
The media's here.

09:00.500 --> 09:03.458
So great.
You're not fake news.

09:03.542 --> 09:04.667
You're real news.

09:04.750 --> 09:07.709
Oh, look!
It's Rachel Maddow. Yay!

09:07.792 --> 09:09.625
And is that
Anderson Cooper I see?

09:09.709 --> 09:11.959
Handsome Andy...
That's what I call him.

09:12.041 --> 09:13.583
We're really
hitting it off, right?

09:13.667 --> 09:15.792
Oh, hey, what do you say
we start over,

09:15.875 --> 09:18.625
and you report that I'm
the best president in history?

09:18.709 --> 09:20.458
Sir, all that
we can promise

09:20.542 --> 09:23.583
is that we will report
the facts as we see them.

09:25.083 --> 09:27.750
Screw you, Cooper, and
your Judi Dench haircut!

09:27.834 --> 09:30.750
Maddow, how many blazers
do you own?! All of 'em?!

09:30.834 --> 09:32.083
Dickerson,
just how many people

09:32.166 --> 09:34.583
have you drowned in those
beautiful blue eyes?

09:34.667 --> 09:36.875
Why can't you all
be like Hannity and
just report the facts?

09:36.959 --> 09:40.500
Donald Trump's sperm would
impregnate a block of gypsum!

09:40.583 --> 09:42.458
Sir, if I may,
we are journalists, damn it,

09:42.542 --> 09:44.458
and that means we hold
the powerful accountable

09:44.542 --> 09:46.083
as long as it earns
our parent companies

09:46.166 --> 09:47.166
tanker ships
full of cash.

09:47.250 --> 09:48.709
All right, bribe time.

09:48.792 --> 09:50.291
How many buckets of chicken will
it take to buy your opinions?

09:50.375 --> 09:51.959
I have all kinds...
Barbecue, fried.

09:52.041 --> 09:53.375
Forget it.
I'll make a list.

09:53.458 --> 09:55.417
I was gonna do it at
some point today, anyway.

09:55.500 --> 09:59.500
If you want to look composed
around any old world leader,

09:59.583 --> 10:01.417
I would recommend
a shot of Botox.

10:01.500 --> 10:02.834
But this is Donald Trump,

10:02.917 --> 10:04.959
so we need to kill
your face outright.

10:05.041 --> 10:06.291
Now watch the screen.

10:06.375 --> 10:08.208
Ooh. Beautiful deer.

10:08.291 --> 10:10.125
What the...

10:10.208 --> 10:12.083
Aah!

10:12.166 --> 10:13.000
Why would you show me this?!

10:13.083 --> 10:15.709
Your husband's capable
of saying worse.

10:15.792 --> 10:17.333
Now deaden that face.

10:17.417 --> 10:18.375
At least the driver
was not injured.

10:18.458 --> 10:19.792
Oh, my God!

10:19.875 --> 10:21.333
- No, no, no!
- Oh, my God!

10:21.417 --> 10:23.333
That is the worst thing
I've ever seen!

10:23.417 --> 10:24.834
Oh, he's in surgery.

10:24.917 --> 10:26.542
He's... He's going to
be okay, right, Sarah?

10:26.625 --> 10:29.417
- Right?
- Watch the screen.

10:29.500 --> 10:31.291
The doctor's a clown.

10:31.375 --> 10:32.917
And a cannibal!

10:33.000 --> 10:35.041
N-o-o-o-o!!

10:35.125 --> 10:36.542
Remember the drill...

10:36.625 --> 10:38.542
You tell the press that I'm
pen pals with some poor kid

10:38.625 --> 10:41.625
and I give him
tons of advice and money.

10:41.709 --> 10:42.834
Classic Trump move...

10:42.917 --> 10:46.542
Plant a positive story and
watch the great press come in.

10:46.625 --> 10:47.917
CNN tip line.
How can I help you?

10:48.000 --> 10:51.875
Hi. Uh, I'm 9 years old,
and President Trump calls me

10:51.959 --> 10:54.667
every morning to give me
advice and lots of money.

10:54.750 --> 10:57.834
Uh-huh. Nice story. And
what's your name, young man?

10:57.917 --> 10:59.375
Uh, Guy Callmaker?

10:59.458 --> 11:01.750
Oh, fuck, crap, shit!

11:01.834 --> 11:03.041
They practically
put me on trial!

11:03.125 --> 11:06.709
It's all right. Calm down
while Eric gives it a shot.

11:06.792 --> 11:09.083
Well, should be
pretty easy for me.

11:09.166 --> 11:11.917
6th grade, I played a yellow
brick in "Wizard of Oz,"

11:12.000 --> 11:13.709
so pretty much
got that down.

11:13.792 --> 11:16.875
CNN tip line.
How can I help you?

11:16.959 --> 11:22.917
Uh, h-hello.
I'm... Johnny... P-Phonedialer.

11:23.000 --> 11:25.959
I'm a brick, and I would
like to plant a story!

11:26.041 --> 11:28.333
Crap!

11:28.417 --> 11:29.166
Jesus Christ.

11:29.250 --> 11:31.000
It's all right.
Just calm down.

11:31.083 --> 11:32.875
Let's let Don Junior
try it again.

11:32.959 --> 11:37.083
I didn't realize how much
your face showed emotion,

11:37.166 --> 11:38.750
so your training
will be more intense,

11:38.834 --> 11:40.417
starting at the end
of this sentence.

11:40.500 --> 11:42.750
Oh, no.
What's going to happen?

11:42.834 --> 11:47.000
- Ted Cruz!
- N-o-o-o-o-o-o-o-o-o!!

11:47.083 --> 11:50.000
Looking beautiful, as always,
Madam First Lady!

11:50.083 --> 11:52.041
Sarah and I
worked out a deal.

11:52.125 --> 11:53.959
She'll circle a bunch
of cars in the desert

11:54.041 --> 11:56.709
so I can fight Mike Pence
for the Vice Presidency,

11:56.792 --> 11:59.166
and I'll talk about things
like I'm the only man on Earth

11:59.250 --> 12:00.583
who grows hair
into his body.

12:00.667 --> 12:05.041
That's right...
Every hair is ingrown!

12:05.125 --> 12:05.959
Dermatologists
can't explain it,

12:06.041 --> 12:09.458
theologists curse it,
and cats hiss at it.

12:09.542 --> 12:10.792
I don't want
to do this anymore!

12:10.875 --> 12:13.792
We are at war with the media,
and war is hell.

12:13.875 --> 12:14.792
Kill me now!

12:14.875 --> 12:17.583
Remember, your face
should be as lifeless

12:17.667 --> 12:19.625
as a dog after your
brother shoots it.

12:19.709 --> 12:20.959
Do it, Melania.

12:21.041 --> 12:23.959
Okay.
I'll try.

12:24.041 --> 12:25.500
You ever think
about how words

12:25.583 --> 12:27.959
don't sound as disturbing
if you sing them?

12:28.041 --> 12:29.291
♪ Organ failure ♪

12:29.375 --> 12:31.291
♪ Shattered pelvis ♪

12:31.375 --> 12:33.291
♪ Internal hair! ♪

12:33.375 --> 12:34.667
Ted Cruz! Ted Cruz!

12:36.333 --> 12:37.625
This is the footage
that explains

12:37.709 --> 12:39.417
the totality
of the threat, sir.

